  "title": "Business Consultant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>·       Support the rollout and growth of fintech products in the Bangladesh market, from planning through execution</p><p>·       Analyse market performance, user behaviour, and financial metrics to provide data-driven business recommendations</p><p>·       Keep close track of market performance, user trends, and financial results, and turn data into practical business insights</p><p>·       Adapt go-to-market and partnership strategies to suit local regulations, customer behaviour, and market realities</p><p>·       Work closely with product, engineering, operations, compliance, and business development teams to ensure solutions are fit for the local market</p><p>·       Conduct market, competitor, and regulatory analysis to identify growth opportunities and risks</p><p>·       Support stakeholder engagement with partners, regulators, and internal teams to drive execution excellence</p><p>·       Share market insights and best practices with regional and global consulting teams</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>·       Minimum 5 years of experience in fintech, financial services, technology consulting, or high-growth tech environments</p><p>·       Strong business and financial acumen with a data-driven, analytical mindset</p><p>·       Experience working in emerging markets; exposure to Bangladesh or South Asia is a strong advantage</p><p>·       Familiar with digital payments, remittance, mobile money, or financial inclusion products</p><p>·       Hands-on, adaptable, and willing to get into the details when needed</p><p>·       Strong communication skills and able to work with different teams and stakeholders</p><p>·       Fluent in English; Bangla (will need to liaise and deal with Bangladesh local stakeholders) is a strong advantage</p><p><em><strong>All Successful candidates can expect a very competitive remuneration package and a comprehensive range of benefits.</strong></em></p><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</em></p><p>People Profilers Pte Ltd, 20 Cecil Street, #08-09 PLUS Building, Singapore 049705<em> </em></p><p> Tel: <strong>6950 9748 </strong></p><p><a href=\"http://www.peopleprofilers.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em><strong>http://www.peopleprofilers.com</strong></em></a><u><em><strong></strong></em></u></p><p><a href=\"mailto:debbie@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em><strong>debbie@peopleprofilers.com</strong></em></a></p><p><strong>Consultant in charge: So Boon Shyen, Debbie</strong></p><p><strong>EA Licence Number: 02C4944</strong></p><p><strong>Registration Number: R1111376</strong></p>",
